\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\align center
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename figures/decay_curves.png
	lyxscale 20
	width 60text%
	rotateAngle 90

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Given this information, the neighborhoods used to identify hotspots are
 defined by the following metrics:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Rook Contiguity (
\begin_inset ERT
