\end_layout

\end_inset

) to capture variance in intensity impact along the fiscal resources dimension.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Term
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

3c includes a single variable, gross state product in the previous year
 (
\begin_inset ERT
status open

