 is certainly a busy visual display of variation in cluster distances.
 The takeway, however, is not a precise estimate of variation.
 Rather, this chart shows that the distribution of values differs markedly
 by calculation method.
 To the extent that these distributions neither perfectly overlap nor exhibit
 fixed relationships observed in all counties, it can be inferred that the
 results of this analysis may be sensitive to calculation methods.
 That being said, consistent findings from these models in spite of this
 variation would be strong evidence in support of a real relationship existing
