_growth & 0.100 & 0.011 & 0.079$^{*}$ 
\backslash

\backslash
    & (0.062) & (0.047) & (0.048) 
\backslash

\backslash
    pcintgov & $-$0.00003$^{*}$ & $-$0.00004$^{***}$ & $-$0.00003$^{**}$ 
